# Planning the app

The first step is to layout the structure and plan which components you might need.

We need a root component to hold everything. Then we need a header. we will need to outsource the header.

# Shopping list

We need a shopping list component and shopping list edit component. 

# Recipe Book

We need a recipe list, recipe item, and recipe detail.

Each compoment should hold business logic. And each component focuses on one main topic.

# Models

Which data will we use in this app. We need some representation for our ingredients. 